Package: urxinput
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Vince Shields
Depends: xinput
Description: Terminal UI for managing XInput devices
 urxinput provides a terminal-based user interface for enabling and
 disabling XInput devices. It allows easy management of input devices
 such as mice, keyboards, and touchpads through a simple ncurses-like
 interface powered by urwid.
